        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/266250/8296_266250_000052_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "\"Yes, it is from his kind hand all our blessings come.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_266250_000057_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/266250/8296_266250_000057_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "\"Yes, these are what my dear mother played with when she was a little girl like Elsie and Vi\" said mamma.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_266250_000057_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/266250/8296_266250_000057_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "\"You may look at them.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_266250_000062_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/266250/8296_266250_000062_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "They had heard the story-all that mamma and mammy could tell-many times, but it never lost its charm.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_266250_000063_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/266250/8296_266250_000063_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "\"Yes, dears, I will: I love to think and speak of her,\" Elsie said, sitting down in a low chair while they gathered closely round her, the older two, one on each side, the others leaning upon her lap.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
