        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "An acquaintance took him to call upon a young lady friend of his, to whom Elsie Grayson was paying a visit, and the two were in the drawing room together when the young men entered.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_266250_000086_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/266250/8296_266250_000086_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "\"What did you think the first minute you saw her, grandpa?\" asked Eddie.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_266250_000092_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/266250/8296_266250_000092_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "\"But to go on with my story.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_266250_000092_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/266250/8296_266250_000092_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "I could not keep away from my charmer, and for the next few weeks we saw each other daily.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_266250_000093_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/266250/8296_266250_000093_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "\"I asked her to be my own little wife and she consented.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_266250_000094_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/266250/8296_266250_000094_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "\"Her guardian was away in a distant city and knew nothing about the matter.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_266250_000098_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/266250/8296_266250_000098_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "mr Dinsmore's voice faltered.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_266250_000099_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/266250/8296_266250_000099_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "\"We never saw each other again.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_266250_000099_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/266250/8296_266250_000099_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "When I went back in the morning the house was closed and quite deserted; not even a servant in it, and I knew not where to look for my lost wife.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_266250_000100_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/266250/8296_266250_000100_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "\"I went back to my hotel and there found my father waiting for me in my room.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_266250_000100_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/266250/8296_266250_000100_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "He was very angry about my marriage, the news of which had brought him from home.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_266250_000100_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/266250/8296_266250_000100_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "He made me go back with him at once and sent me North to college.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_266250_000103_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/266250/8296_266250_000103_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "But see here! will not these do quite as well?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_266250_000104_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/266250/8296_266250_000104_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "And rising, mrs Travilla opened the door of another closet displaying to the children's delighted eyes other toys as fine and in as great profusion and variety as those she considered sacred to her mother's memory.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_266250_000106_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/266250/8296_266250_000106_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "And now we will lock the doors and go down to dress for dinner.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_266250_000106_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/266250/8296_266250_000106_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "The first bell is ringing.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000000_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000000_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "The French, however, were great adventurers by nature, and Napoleon, changing the map of Europe, could not keep his fingers from North America.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000000_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000000_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "He planned to win back the New France that had been given away.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000000_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000000_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "Spain was weak, and Napoleon traded a small province in Italy for the great tract of Louisiana.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000000_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000000_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "He meant to colonize and fortify this splendid empire, but before it could be done enemies gathered against his eagles at home, and to save his European throne he had to forsake his western colony.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000002_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000002_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "Scarcely anything was known of Louisiana, except the stories told by a few hunters.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000004_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000004_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "As they went up the river they frequently met canoes loaded with furs coming down.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000004_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000004_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "Captain Lewis wrote down many of their curious traditions.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000004_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000004_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "The explorers found, however, that since the value of beaver skins had risen in trade with the white men, these Indians were not so particular in their reverence for their relatives.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000006_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000006_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "The Indians were friendly and each day taught the white men something new.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000006_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000006_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "Each tribe differed in some way from its neighbors.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000006_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000006_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "For the first time the explorers found among the Rickarees eight sided earth covered lodges, and basket shaped boats made of interwoven boughs covered with buffalo skins.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000007_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000007_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "Game was plentiful as they went farther up the Missouri River.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000007_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000007_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "They traveled rapidly until the approach of cold weather decided them to establish winter quarters on october twenty seventh.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000009_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000009_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "Almost every day hunting parties left the camp and brought back buffaloes.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "The weather grew very cold in December, and several times the thermometer fell to forty degrees below zero.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000011_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000011_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "Occasionally they came upon a deserted Indian camp, but in this northern territory they found few roving tribes.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000011_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000011_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "Captain Lewis christened the stream Porcupine River.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000012_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000012_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "The country along this stream was bare for some distance, with gradually rising hills beyond.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000013_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000013_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "They dragged him to shore, and found that eight balls had gone through him in different directions.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000013_000013",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000013_000013.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "The boat would have turned upside down but for the resistance of the canvas awning.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000013_000014",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000013_000014.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "The other boats hastened to the rescue, righted the canoe, and by baling her out kept her from sinking.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000013_000015",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000013_000015.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "They rowed the canoe to shore and the cargo was saved.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000014_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000014_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "Their way of hunting was to select one of the most active braves, and disguise him by tying a buffalo skin around his body, fastening the skin of the head, with ears and horns, over the head of the brave.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000014_000008",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000014_000008.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "The other hunters would steal back of the herd, and at a given signal chase them.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000014_000011",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000014_000011.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "The buffaloes in front could not stop being driven on by those behind, who in their turn would be closely pursued by the hunters.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000014_000013",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000014_000013.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "This method of hunting was very extravagant, but at that time the Indians had no thought of preserving the buffaloes.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000016_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000016_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "With great presence of mind the man did this, and getting a foothold, raised himself on his knees.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000018_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000018_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "The rest of the river shot forward with greater force, and, being broken by projecting rocks, sent clouds of foam into the air.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000019_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000019_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "Fortunately they found a small creek at the foot of the falls, and by this they were able to reach the highlands.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000019_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/8296/279865/8296_279865_000019_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-8296",
        "content": "They decided to leave one of their boats behind, and use its mast for two axle trees.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-8296_279865_000020_000000",
